{"tid":2410760,"cid":36,"subCid":0,"title":"［真人真事］達子我發夢夢到呵緊尿，點知現實真係瀨咗尿","createTime":"2021-02-17T00:50:57.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-17T14:06:58.000Z","uid":38604,"like":0,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"0fbee657b003acb00816c32c6e6b9a88bda386b5","tid":2410760,"uid":38604,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-17T00:50:57.000Z","msg":"首先，達子我非失禁，但達子我尋晚明明呵清哂d尿先訓，點知訓訓下竟然夢到自己呵緊尿，達子我當下就即刻醒咗，但又好眼訓之下就選擇繼續訓，但訓訓下又夢到自己呵尿，同埋夢中d尿射到自己，仲feel到暖暖地，但達子我都選擇繼續訓，最尾達子我終於忍唔住起身去呵尿，點知發覺自己成條底褲已經濕哂，再返去睇下張床，發現張床個patpat位置一噠水跡同尿味<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n估唔到達子我都成35歲人，竟然仲會瀨尿，搞到達子今朝早要請病假，依家洗緊床單同條底褲<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />同埋陣間仲要出去睇醫生<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2c3e75d8c93c99a9b418a1245b4167b9f23ef453","tid":2410760,"uid":314029,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-17T01:07:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/06/14/051915_3cc83a2e872550837dd75db4a932d323.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F06%2F14%2F051915_3cc83a2e872550837dd75db4a932d323.jpg&h=d6646d2d&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"8cfec736d47cb1f854de222d301bfccb518d2c05","tid":2410760,"uid":382485,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-17T01:07:48.000Z","msg":"正常 大家都會<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"877b1bb6b514a1185e9b09b6d79f1966d5e1a30f","tid":2410760,"uid":248290,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-17T14:06:58.000Z","msg":"夢遺 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}